          "Ancilla 9"
        ],
        [],
        [
          "Who You Know",
          "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        ],
        [
          "Yasmin the Black",
          "This Black Hand warlock wants to turn the old Tremere Chantry into a magical stronghold for the Sabbat"
        ],
        [
          "Kathrine \"Katie\" Ford",
          "A Black Hand infilitrator recently returned from spying on the Camarilla"
        ],
        [
          "Bishop Cicatriz",
          "The war leader of Tijuana refuses to guarantee the safety of any Sabbat crossing north until the Werewloves are dealt with on the border."
        ],
        [
          "Chalupavka",
          "Rival for Archbishop: A monstrous Tzimsce Elder from Peru. She has strong ties to the Black Hand"
        ],
        [
          "Starting Goals",
          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "The high prescence of the inquistion is problematic, you'd like to find a way to kill as many of them as possible so the Black Hand has a way to get into the new city."
        ],
        [
          "You know that your sire and his pals are in town, and they are looking for some high valued targets. You know how to get in touch with them, and maybe if you can get some of these heavy hitting inquisitioners and packs away it will clear the path."
        ],
        [
          "You don't have an interest in the Chantry, but your whole pack is up in arms about getting inside for their own goals, maybe you can find something a little meatier for them to throw their weight into."
        ],
